      "text": [
        " : فِي جُعْلِ اَلْآبِقِ \"إِنَّ اَلْمُسْلِمَ يُرَدُّ عَلَى اَلْمُسْلِمِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3539 - Ghiyath ibn Ibrahim al-Darimi narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as):\nImam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said regarding the reward for capturing a runaway slave:\n\"Indeed, the Muslim should be returned to the Muslim.\""
        ]
      }
